Apache Flex SDK Installer 2.0
1.  If you have previously installed a release candidate (RC) version of  InstallApacheFlex, you need to uninstall it first.  And then run the downoaded installer file.  
2.  From Flex 4.9 onwards, the Text Layout Framework (TLF) is part of the Flex SDK.  So the installer does not download is separately anymore.  

Apache Flex Installer SDK 1.0

1.  If you have previously installed a pre-release version of  InstallApacheFlex, you need to uninstall it first.  And then run the downoaded installer file.  